= rumbleboard -- because in the heat of the rumble you want to see blood

rumbleboard is a sinatra app to bring the competition of RailsRumble to a spectator audience. 

== Scorekeeping

RumbleBoard keeps score via a set of carefully chosen metrics that have been scientifically proven to be accurate under several blind and a handful of drunk studies.

* First team to respond to http request on their subdomain 
 500 points
 
* First team to develop user interaction 

 500 points
 
* digital asset depth
 10 points per mg



